snippet.title: #agiftforAmber: My video message and story for Amber Heard.
snippet.description:
This is my end of the year video message and story I have for Amber Heard, as an incredible from Amber's fanbase wanted us all to do messages and creative projects of support for Amber after all her continued recent dramatic ordeals surrounding her divorce. I made this video to tell Amber she is capable of far more than she could realize, and her future, once she gets past this, is going to be full of more amazing possiblies than ever. As always, this message is forever always in support of The Playboy Club and that it's hostage held episodes are released at last. This message is one of two submissions with both a video and a written essay explaining this as well, and I do hope you enjoy both!

The Susan Belle/iSpec Essay for Amber-
